::Zardus/Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Zardus frowns as Feline walks off to sit down at a table, obvioustly 
expecting him to give her a drink. While he didn't mind her touching him, he 
did mind having to work for other bots. Zardus walks over to the food 
replicator, making two drinks, which he carries off to the table.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica grins as Zardus places one of the drinks in front of Feline. He 
chuckles quetly. "Gee, none for us, Zardus?" he says, still chuckling, "I'm 
offended."

Zardus growls at the other bot, the threatening look in the Alliance 
commander's eyes shutting Reptilica up. "I trust you have other duties, 
Reptilica."

Reptilica shakes his head. "Nope, I'm on break."

"Good," Zardus says, his voice threatening, "Then you can clean the mechfluid 
out of the torture chambers."

Reptilica sighs, getting up and walking off. Zardus sits down in his seat, 
putting his own drink on the table.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer chuckles at the scene between Zardus and Reptilica, leaning closer 
to Feline.

"So," he says, trying to start conversation, "How do you like the Alliance so 
far?"
